hentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8133,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/khayr-ummah-lil-nas-companions\/","url_meta":{"origin":18477,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Best nation raised up for people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa'id ibn Jubary reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Allah Almighty said: You are the best nation brought forth for people\u00a0(3:110). They are those who emigrated with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, from Mecca to Medina.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 3311 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19322,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/14\/renew-faith-often\/","url_meta":{"origin":18477,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Renew belief by declaring Allah is One","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Hurai